/** @format */

    webiste: "",
    ger_email: "",
    billing_email: "",

    suite: "",
    city: "",
    state: "",
    zip: 0,
    plus_4: 0,

    client_no: 0,
    f_name: "",
    l_name: "",
    dob: null,
    ssn: 0,
    mobile_no: 0,
    home_no: 0,
    office_no: 0,
    fax_no: 0,
    other_no: 0,
    email_1: "",
    email_2: "",
    email_3: "",

    street2: "",
    suite2: "",
    city2: "",
    state2: "",

    memmber: "",

    e.preventDefault();

        sx={{

          margin="normal"
          variant="outlined"
          name="discount"
          label="discount"

        />
        <TextField
          size="small"
          margin="normal"
          variant="outlined"
          name="discount"
          label="discount"
          type="text"
          onChange={(e) => onChange(e)}
          id="discount"
          autoComplete="discount"
        />
        <TextField
          size="small"
          margin="normal"
          variant="outlined"
          name="discount"
          label="discount"
          type="text"
          onChange={(e) => onChange(e)}

        <TextField

        <TextField

        <TextField

        <TextField

};

export default Contact;
